         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Society for Geography etc. at Darmstadt ¶ Esteemed Sir, ¶  ¶ It is my special pleasure to notify you, that the Council of our Society, ¶  in which you have frequently taken such a kindly interest, has...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">62.04.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From L. Ewald</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M106, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Verein für Erdkunde etc.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">zu Darmstadt</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochgeehrtester Herr!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es gereicht mir zum besonderen Vergnügen, Sie zu benachrichtigen, dass der Vorstand unseres Vereins, für welchen Sie vielfach freundliche Theilnahme gezeigt haben, Sie unter die Zahl seiner correspondirenden Mitglieder aufgenommen hat. Demgemäss beehre ich mich, Ihnen hierbei im Auftrage des Vorstandes das Diplom über diese Ernennung mit der Bitte zu übersenden, dem Vereine auch fernerhin Ihr Wohlwollen zu bewahren.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit der ausgezeichnetesten Hochachtung</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr ganz ergebenster</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>L. Ewald</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Darmstadt, 6. April 1862.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">Society for Geography etc. at Darmstadt</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is my special pleasure to notify you, that the Council of our Society,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Society for Geography and Related Sciences [Verein für Erdkunde und Verwandte Wissenschaften]. Darmstadt.</p>
               </note> in which you have frequently taken such a kindly interest, has elected you as a corresponding member. Accordingly I have the honour to send you on behalf of the Council the enclosed certificate<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Verein für Erdkunde und Verwandte Wissenschaften zu Darmstadt to M, 11 January 1862.</p>
               </note> regarding this election with the request that you may continue to favour us with your goodwill.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With the most singular respect</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your most humble</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>L. Ewald.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Darmstadt, 6 April 1862.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
